    "with the density ρ, velocity u, external force b, and Cauchy stress tensor σ.",
    "The components of the Cauchy stress tensor depend on the material model.",
    "For the temperature-dependent viscous model, we employ the strongly coupled, steady, incompressible Navier-Stokes equations together with the heat equation.",
    "Implementation details, including stabilization techniques, are provided in (González et al., 2023; González, 2023).",
    "We use the Galerkin/least-squares stabilization to stabilize the finite element method."
